      <h1 class='title'>Sending domestic freezing orders</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='grand-committee-report-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 03 February 2003 vol 644 c28GC</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_28gc' title='Col. 28GC &mdash; HL Deb 03 February 2003 vol 644 c28GC' name='column_28gc' href='#column_28gc' rel='bookmark'>28GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00972'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_157' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        11C (1) If a certificate is made under paragraph 11B, the restraint order and the certificate are to be sent to the Secretary of State for forwarding to&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) a court exercising jurisdiction in the place where the property is situated, or</li>
        <li>(b) any authority recognised by the government of the participating country as the appropriate authority for receiving orders of that kind.</li></ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00973'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_158' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (2) The restraint order and the certificate must be accompanied by a forfeiture order, unless the certificate indicates when the court expects a forfeiture order to be sent.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00974'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_159' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (3) The certificate must include a translation of it into an appropriate language of the participating country (if that language is not English).
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00975'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_160' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (4) The certificate must be signed by or on behalf of the court and must include a statement as to the accuracy of the information given in it.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00976'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_161' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The signature may be an electronic signature.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0644P0-00977'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0644P0_20030203_GCR_162' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (5) If the restraint order and the certificate are not accompanied by a forfeiture order, but a forfeiture order is subsequently made, it is to be sent to the Secretary of State for forwarding as mentioned in sub-paragraph (1).
      </p>
      <ol class='xoxo'>
        
      </ol>
      
